Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:21.88,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,485)\fad(0,1080)\bord0\blur5\c&H3E3E3E&\3c&H788C8F&\alpha&HFF&\t(0,920,2,\alpha&H00&)\t(0,870,2,\blur1.5)\t(870,870,\bord0.2\blur1.5)\t(870,920,\bord0.2\blur2)\t(4380,4420,\bord0.2\blur1.5)\t(4420,4420,\bord0)\t(4420,5460,\blur5)\t(4960,5380,\c&H08947C&)}病歷25
